body: I managed to build pip package from master branch on a Raspbian Pi 3 B running Raspbian and ran the [label_image using Python TF Lite binding](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/examples/python/label_image.md) example without problem. So, this should be some kind of compilation flag problem when these pip packages were built.
